<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wǒ men gè rén yào huǐ gǎi 迦南437</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men gè rén yào huǐ gǎi, fèng zhǔ de míng shòu xǐ,
 shǐ wǒ men de zuì dé shè, bì lǐng shòu suǒ cì de shèng líng,\001
 zhè yīng xǔ shì shén gěi, wǒ men hé ér nǚ,
 wǒ men hé ér nǚ, hái yǒu yuǎn fāng liú làng de rén.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>437</hymn_number>
</song>